io.sphere.sdk.queries

Interface QueryDsl<T,C extends QueryDsl<T,C>>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of the query result
    C - type of the class implementing this class
    All Superinterfaces:
    ExpansionPathContainer<T>, Query<T>, ReferenceExpansionDsl<T,C>, ReferenceExpansionSupport<T>, ResourceQuery<T>, SphereRequest<PagedQueryResult<T>>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ApiClientQuery, CartDiscountQuery, CartInStoreQuery, CartQuery, CategoryQuery, ChannelQuery, CustomerGroupQuery, CustomerInStoreQuery, CustomerQuery, CustomObjectQuery<T>, DiscountCodeQuery, ExtensionQuery, InventoryEntryQuery, JsonNodeQuery, MessageQuery, MetaModelQueryDsl<T,C,Q,E>, OrderEditQuery, OrderInStoreQuery, OrderQuery, PaymentQuery, ProductDiscountQuery, ProductProjectionQuery, ProductQuery, ProductTypeQuery, ReviewQuery, ShippingMethodQuery, ShoppingListInStoreQuery, ShoppingListQuery, StateQuery, StoreQuery, SubscriptionQuery, TaxCategoryQuery, TypeQuery, ZoneQuery
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MetaModelQueryDslImpl

    public interface QueryDsl<T,C extends QueryDsl<T,C>>
extends ResourceQuery<T>, ReferenceExpansionDsl<T,C>
    Query request interface for immutable value classes which can copy themselves with modified fields.

      • withFetchTotal

        C withFetchTotal(boolean fetchTotal)
        Enables/disables a flag it the total amount of items should be counted.

        If fetchTotal is true then PagedQueryResult.getTotal() is null.

        Parameters:
        fetchTotal - enable the total count if true (default on the construction of the QueryDsl).
        Returns:
        the same QueryDsl as this instance but with the updated flag
